let me explain in simple way:

-Set of conceptual structure and guidelines used to build something useful.
-Softwares that are developed to build applications.
-Collection of tools designed to help to create your project so you do not need to start from scratch.

ðŸ”»#Framework: May include predefined classes, funtions that can be used to process input, manage hardware devices, interact with system architecture.

ðŸ”»-Purpose: Allow Developers to focus on business logic and features of their applicaation rather than writing codes from scratch.

